1490 REM BOX OUTLINE
1500 REM BX,BY = BOX POSITION
1510 REM BH,BW = BOX HEIGHT & WIDTH
1520 REM BC$ = CHARACTER FOR BOX EDGE
1530 REM MC10: BR$="":FOR BR=1TOBW:BR$=BR$+BC$:NEXT
1540 REM COCO/DRAGON: BR$=STRING$(BW,BC$)
1550 BR$=STRING$(BW,BC$)
1560 ?@BX+((BY+1)*32),BR$;
1570 ?@BX+((BY+BH)*32),BR$;
