1620 REM BX,BY = BOX POSITION
1630 REM BH,BW = BOX HEIGHT & WIDTH
1640 REM BC$ = CHARACTER FOR BOX
1650 REM MC10: BR$="":FOR BR=1TOBW:BR$=BR$+BC$:NEXT
